(3909, 724, 'session_1_content', '<p style="font-size: 26px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 30px;">EASE</span> </strong>stock a large range of air starter motors,underground mining tools and equipment,<strong>air operated diaphragm pumps</strong><span style="font-weight: bold;">,</span> hand held air tools, compressors and pneumatic accessories.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 20px;"><a class="various fancybox.iframe" href="http://www.youtube.com/v/4tS88S6em8Y?fs=1&amp;autoplay=1"><img src="http://dev.dusted.com.au/dev_ease_woo/wp-content/themes/main/images/button-youtube.jpg" alt="" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 20px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px;">EASE</span> </strong>can provide sales and speciality services of all air operated equipment from a basic hand held air toll through to roof bolters and rib drills - including operating Queensland''s only <strong><span style="font-size: 20px;">Rambor Test Bench</span></strong> offering customers a specialised form of roof bolter testing - including <strong><span style="font-size: 20px;">motor rotation and leg force testing</span></strong> of all underground mining roof bolters!</p>'),
(3910, 724, 'session_1_image_background', 'http://dev.dusted.com.au/dev_ease_woo/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/home-bg-1.png'),
(3911, 724, 'session_2_content', '<p style="font-size: 28px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 30px;">EASE</span> </strong>operate <strong><span style="font-size: 30px;">QLD’s</span> </strong>only</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 28px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 30px;">RAMBOR / PPK Firefly Mining Equipment</span></strong>\r\n<strong> <span style="font-size: 30px;">Roofbolter Test Bench </span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 20px;">Offering customers a specialised and <span style="font-weight: bold;">reliable method</span>\r\nof roof bolter testing including motor rotation and\r\n<strong>complete leg for testing</strong><span style="font-weight: bold;">.</span></p>\r\n<a class="various fancybox.iframe" href="http://www.youtube.com/v/4tS88S6em8Y?fs=1&amp;autoplay=1"><img src="http://dev.dusted.com.au/dev_ease_woo/wp-content/themes/main/images/play-icon.png" alt="" /></a>'),
(3912, 724, 'session_2_image_background', 'http://dev.dusted.com.au/dev_ease_woo/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/bg-2.jpg'),
(3913, 724, 'session_3_content', '<p style="font-size: 26px; text-align: right; line-height: 35px;"><strong><span class="bold" style="font-size: 28px;">EASE</span> </strong>is a member of the I.S.G. - Industrial\r\nSupply Group. The I.S.G. is a coalition\r\nof major independent industrial\r\nsupply companies servicing\r\ncustomers Australia wide,\r\nwith the proven capacity\r\nto service <strong><span class="bold">national</span></strong>\r\n<strong> <span class="bold">accounts</span></strong><span class="bold" style="font-weight: bold;">.</span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-top: 20px; font-size: 28px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 140px;"><a style="color: white;"><strong><span class="bold" style="font-size: 30px;">Read</span> </strong>our <strong><span class="bold" style="font-size: 30px;">Capability Statement</span></strong> </a><a class="btn-circle btn-circle-no-border" style="margin-left: 40px; background-color: orange;" href="#">+</a></p>'),
(3914, 724, 'session_3_image_background', 'http://dev.dusted.com.au/dev_ease_woo/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/bg-3_04.jpg'),
(3915, 724, 'session_4_content', '<p class="col-md-10" style="font-size: 20px; color: #005596; text-align: left;"><img src="http://dev.dusted.com.au/dev_ease_woo/wp-content/themes/main/images/watch.png" alt="" /></p>\r\nEmerald Air Starters &amp; Equipment, or EASE as our customers know us are the sole authorised Emerald distributor for quality Atlas-Copco Compressors and Tools, including the new Oil-injected Rotary Screw Compressor range.\r\n<p class="col-md-2"><img style="position: absolute; top: -150px; left: 0;" src="http://dev.dusted.com.au/dev_ease_woo/wp-content/themes/main/images/pic1.png" alt="" /></p>'),
